Package com.epam.aircompany.bean

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Airplane
    The Class Airplane is a Java Bean that stores data on model and board number of the airplane.
    AirplaneType
    The Class AirplaneType is a Java Bean that stores data on model of the airplane.
    Airport
    The Class Airport is a Java Bean that contains a name of the airport and its international codes.
    City
    The Class City is a Java Bean that contains a name of the city in which the airport is located.
    CompositionCrew
    The Class CompositionCrew is a Java Bean that contains information on number of crew members for specific type of the airplane.
    Crew
    The Class Crew is a Java Bean that contains information on crew of the airplane.
    Employee
    The Class Employee is a Java Bean that contains information on a position and start date of operation.
    Entity
    Abstract Class Entity is a Java Bean that is a superclass to all other entity classes.
    Person
    The Class Person is a Java Bean that contains personal information on the employee, superclass for the class Employee.
    Position
    The Class Position is a Java Bean that contains a job title.
    Route
    The Class Route is a Java Bean that contains information on number of flight, date/time of embarkation and an arrival, airport of departure and an arrival, the airplane, crew.
